{"tid":2241640,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"其實著格仔恤衫唔一定= IT男或者毒男","createTime":"2020-10-13T12:23:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-19T16:58:30.000Z","uid":227650,"like":4,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"c233bb4771fd84ad1c097c7479b918b22350c653","tid":2241640,"uid":227650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T12:23:58.000Z","msg":"我覺得格仔恤衫好似俾人定咗型咁<br />\n<br />\n格仔恤衫都有唔同嘅cutting、顏色， 最重要係啱size同埋顏色要揀得好小心，揀得啱嘅話其實可以好型。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jrJsBAD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjrJsBAD.jpg&h=92194f08&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6vg2qt2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6vg2qt2.jpg&h=435b47a6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n84vznt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn84vznt.jpg&h=13ea15f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我自己幾鍾意黑白格仔同埋藍白格仔，感覺容易襯得嚟又唔會毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲有紅黑格仔我都幾鍾意，不過我就覺得紅黑比較容易著得毒啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\np.s 我覺得而家嘅天氣著一件格仔恤衫啱啱好"},{"pid":"7ecd756b4951e24cab49a439d8774e4701abfe86","tid":2241640,"uid":224533,"like":55,"dislike":0,"score":55,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T12:24:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aULR3hQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaULR3hQ.jpg&h=b88129ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6eJoUpw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6eJoUpw.jpg&h=0505f9a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DADDJhR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDADDJhR.jpg&h=41642290&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0094063aa8e227aa18a3abc6fc365e93fca1cf22","tid":2241640,"uid":64345,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T12:26:00.000Z","msg":"最尾都係講樣，係咪呀，哈姆太郎